content:
Zeng Chaoliang is a 3rd-year Ph.D. student in Department of Computer Science and Engineering, Hong Kong University of Science and Technology. He is one of the member of SING lab, supervised by Prof. Kai Chen.
Chaoliang received Bachelor degree with First Class Honors in 2018 from USTC.
